                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Williams</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-05-08">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 8, 1896</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>In case of <hi rend="italic">Competitor</hi>, trial terminated. Prosecuting
                    officer asks penalty death for all, giving precedence to the local law relating
                    to foreigners over the treaty and the protocol in this case. As the court and
                    authorities here agree on this point, I inform you for such diplomatic action
                    you may deem proper. I am preparing remonstrance Captain-General as the superior
                    delegate of Spain in this island.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
